OL,6,FMs Gray was the top civil servant in
OL,7,FStormont's Department of Finance at
OL,8,Fthe outset of the pandemic before she
OL,9,Ftransferred to the Cabinet Office in
OL,10,FLondon in May 2021.
OL,12,FShe was asked to appear before the
OL,13,Finquiry as the only senior ranking
OL,14,Fcivil servant who had experience of
OL,15,Fworking for both the devolved
OL,16,Fadministration in Northern Ireland and
OL,17,Fthe UK Government during the
OL,18,Fcoronavirus emergency.
